  • public class AppboyFeedActivity
extends AppboyBaseFragmentActivity
    The AppboyFeedActivity in an Activity class that displays the Braze News Feed Fragment. This class can be used to integrate the Braze News Feed as an Activity. Note: To integrate the Braze News Feed as a Fragment instead of an Activity, use the AppboyFeedFragment class.
